[30;1m1076 | [0m[35m   of the specified *user* which is sometimes used when a user changes[0m

[30;1m1078 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m1079 | [0m[35m   *respoid* is always :py:const:`None`. *respvalue* is also[0m
[30;1m1080 | [0m[35m   :py:const:`None` unless *newpw* was :py:const:`None`. This requests that[0m

[30;1m654 | [0m[35m            who=who, cred=cred, fileno=sock.fileno(), **kwargs[0m

[30;1m15 | [0m[35m   Dictionary mapping the OIDs of known response controls to the accompanying[0m
[30;1m16 | [0m[35m   :py:class:`ResponseControl` classes. This is used[0m
